reviewText: Love the DVD! My kiddo LOVES Barney and he's on 24/7! This DVD keeps her entertained on car rides. Also love that the DVD gives you the option for continuous repeated play so I don't have to keep messing with it while driving. (Headphones are lifesavers!!)
Awesome DVD. Got is super fast. Exactly as described. Definitely well be checking more out.
My son loved it, definitely would buy again. Quick shipping, item exactly as described. Worth waiting for when my son watches it every day!
